nodes.name: D-ribose 5-phosphate,D-glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate pyridoxal 5'-phosphate-lyase (glutamine-hydrolyzing)
nodes.rxn: D-Ribose 5-phosphate + D-Glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate + L-Glutamine <=> Pyridoxal phosphate + L-Glutamate + 3 H2O + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: pyridoxamine:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: Pyridoxamine + H2O + Oxygen <=> Pyridoxal + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: pyridoxamine-5'-phosphate:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: Pyridoxamine phosphate + H2O + Oxygen <=> Pyridoxal phosphate + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: pyridoxine 5'-phosphate:oxygen oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Pyridoxine phosphate + Oxygen <=> Hydrogen peroxide + Pyridoxal phosphate

nodes.name: 2-(acetamidomethylene)succinate amidohydrolase (deaminating, decarboxylating)
nodes.rxn: 2-(Acetamidomethylene)succinate + 2 H2O <=> Acetate + Succinate semialdehyde + Ammonia + CO2
